Package org.forgerock.cuppa.model

Model for the structure of Cuppa tests.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Hook
    A hook is code that is executed before or after a test is run.
    Test
    Encapsulates the test ('it') function block.
    TestBlock
    Encapsulates the 'describe' and 'when' function blocks and all nested 'describe', 'when' and test ('it') function blocks.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Behaviour
    Controls the behaviour of a test or collection of tests.
